description:
Medical Symposium 3 explores the benefits of nutrition and exercise-induced antioxidants and the racial disparities in COVID-19 death rates. Why is it that African Americans are at a higher risk?

Attend this COVID-19 live online symposium by leading physicians & receive Category 1 CME credits FREE. Learn more and register at awr.org/health
